			<CASNumber>497-19-8</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Soda ash, dense refers to a high bulk density form of sodium carbonate, commonly used in various industrial applications. This product flow details its granular anhydrous form, which has been processed for purity, adherence to industry standards, quality controlled, specific uses such as glass manufacturing or pH regulation, and details the synthetic production route from common salt and limestone via the Solvay process. The description also includes that the substance is typically delivered as a production mix to consumer or bulk availability at a production plant.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">密实型纯碱指的是碳酸钠的一种高堆积密度形式，通常用于各种工业应用。产品流程详述了其颗粒无水形式，经过纯度加工、符合工业标准、质量控制，具体用途包括制造玻璃或调节pH值，以及从普通盐和石灰石出发，通过索尔维方法合成生产的详细路线。该说明还包括物质通常作为生产混合物交付给消费者或在生产工厂批量可用。</common:generalComment>
